thread.title_full: Ace Rental Cars Australia & New Zealand reviewed by Mac Trudy Keene

author: Mac Trudy Keene
title: Mac Trudy Keene
text: We rented a Nissan Tiida for 2 weeks. We found the car acceptible in most ways: the smell of smoking in the car was bad, but acceptible given the age of the car. It was tidy, comfortable, and very economical to run.
